19/10/2005
SEOUL, South Korea -- Romanian President Traian Basescu met with business executives in Seoul on Tuesday (18 October) and invited their companies to invest in Romania. 
Basescu met with managers of Daewoo Shipbuilding and Marine Engineering, Korea Hydro and Nuclear Power, and Samsung Corporation. 
As part of his visit, an agreement on enhanced bilateral co-operation in the IT sector was sealed. 
(Rompres, Nine o'clock - 19/10/05; Asia Pulse - 18/10/05)
